If you use terminal multiplexer like screen , you could easily achieve
that by using below procedule.

Once in screen ...do this

CTRL+a then press ESC=20

Now use the touchpad scrolling and all the text or specific selected
text get copied into the buffer.

Once you finish selecting text ,press ESC again to end the "copy mode"

Then open a file  where you decided to put those
copied text ...once it open then press ]=20

voila! you made it ...

Thanks,
Bhaskar


